# 🎭 Gesture Meme Generator

A real-time AI-powered Gesture Meme Generator built using Python, OpenCV, and MediaPipe. The application detects hand gestures and face landmarks through a webcam and displays a corresponding meme instantly.

## ✨ Features

- 📷 Real-time webcam detection
- ✋ Hand gesture recognition
- 😀 Face Mesh detection
- 🖼️ Displays memes based on detected gestures
- ⚡ Fast and lightweight
- 💻 Built with Python

---

## Technologies Used

- Python
- OpenCV
- MediaPipe
- NumPy

---

## Project Structure

```
gesture-meme/
│
├── main.py
├── memes/
│   ├── rock.jpg
│   ├── paper.jpg
│   ├── scissors.jpg
│   └── thumbsup.jpg
│
└── README.md
```

---

## Installation

### Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Vaishnaviks650/gesture-meme.git
cd gesture-meme
```

### Create a virtual environment

Windows

```bash
python -m venv .venv
```

Activate

```bash
.venv\Scripts\activate
```

---

### Install dependencies

```bash
pip install opencv-python mediapipe numpy
```

---

## Run the project

```bash
python main.py
```

---

## Supported Gestures

| Gesture | Meme |
|----------|------|
| ✊ Rock | Rock Meme |
| ✋ Paper | Paper Meme |
| ✌️ Scissors | Scissors Meme |
| 👍 Thumbs Up | Thumbs Up Meme |

---

## Requirements

- Python 3.11 or Python 3.12 (Recommended)
- Webcam

> **Note:** MediaPipe currently has compatibility issues with Python 3.14. Use Python 3.11 or 3.12 for best results.

